text: There are might be many reasons to a not very good deliverability rate, like message content (e.g. if a message is recognized as a spam because of links, headers, etc.), if many recepients have pressed “it’s a spam” - so what you’ve sent previously with this email and many others. There are many resources on how to improve it. And you can also check with some free domain health checks your domain status and issues to improve.
